          "content": "大口黑鲈的投喂管理对其生长和健康有重要影响。研究表明，投喂频率对大口黑鲈的生长、生理指标和肝脏GH、IGF-I基因表达丰度有显著影响[[33](http://www.aquaticjournal.com/article/doi/10.3724/SP.J.1118.2020.19195?viewType=HTML)]。此外，饲料中添加枯草芽孢杆菌、维生素D3、胆碱等营养物质可以提高大口黑鲈的生长性能和健康状况[[39](https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=B-gnKLjyiTxk4ITQFDMLp52CsYEoSaTh3USB5ktOwvQAjtSSZjW_5J0XEvIC2fYIj4jkOMyOqab0_J4TBTYMDh97VpvLheEXA7p2gUNmHGyhaNAbsRPvGy693cIamAWoGBBYP9hL1KPyz19Bki8VGqQfJ1F9z7kPUfT2QXYdv6GA5s5Oojc_IOgy13g9sbgP&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS)][[44](https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=B-gnKLjyiTxVmNV8bjmOqEJxUillMj2Rx1pBuzFy5CAb69xSQotGwClP_p1mpIeMcd3jj-psXNbHPzhxOF-XBsg5GGU_HzoO1cVcjVyua7o7KP8u5wLCDwFWaElf94nKmZINse-reW1J8Afmin8TQdZwyMZ-gxINbQzIwNxCVBJbJhz5xFoEYpXmAGZ8UsjK&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS)][[47](https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=B-gnKLjyiTzQ7VtgjCb44nb9w1VJEapRGkGHnFkqwW8ejDxDRKVJy_CvsZ8o0g7Jy6c9eitlNDU3fbae6JoBI8r46mi_HBtAuE84bIQifmvpMd0h1d_OGk-hsDZ-IJ5BvkqEozz7tVYITfIkwJ4UdCJwApI224Hh9wZ2zg0fXtfB1-PtXQtH9twvwuTjOrom&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS)][[47](https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=B-gnKLjyiTzQ7VtgjCb44nb9w1VJEapRGkGHnFkqwW8ejDxDRKVJy_CvsZ8o0g7Jy6c9eitlNDU3fbae6JoBI8r46mi_HBtAuE84bIQifmvpMd0h1d_OGk-hsDZ-IJ5BvkqEozz7tVYITfIkwJ4UdCJwApI224Hh9wZ2zg0fXtfB1-PtXQtH9twvwuTjOrom&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS)]。",
